reviewText:
Introduction:Want to get real fun? Loadout is just what you need!

Good:    amazing graphics and physics;
gun customization system is just perfect;
matchmaking system is awesome;
you can win a match without paying something;
a lot of blood and fresh meat for free;
great network optimization (i play it with 500-700ms delay without any lags /Sattelite connection/ ping in Dota 2 is 1200-1600 xD);Bad:    there is no way to get coins and all the stuff in a game without steam/real money (though same thing is in TF2);
players can't host own dedicated servers;
No more updates for PC :-(In total: 9.5 / 10
